branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series MGF low profile guide table integrates a compact cylinder to a large diameter concentric guide sleeve to handle loads applied from any direction providing equal eccentric load resistance through 360&#xb0;. Using the guide sleeve instead of guide rods reduces the unit&apos;s weight by 15% and eliminates eccentric load capacity variances caused by load orientation. An internal non-rotating pin has been added to prevent rotation of the top plate.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The MGF low profile guide table integrates a compact cylinder to a large diameter concentric guide sleeve to handle loads applied from any direction providing equal eccentric load resistance through 360&#xb0;. Using the guide sleeve instead of guide rods reduces the unit&apos;s weight by 15% and eliminates eccentric load capacity variances caused by load orientation. An internal non-rotating pin has been added to prevent rotation of the top plate.
&lt;/p&gt;

